                                              "content": "I see the issue. In the `_handle_insertion` method, it's comparing `line.strip()` with `target` (which is `# Insert here`), but the line contains the tokenized version `__TOKEN__2320496e736572742068657265__`. \n\nWe need to detokenize the line before comparing. Let me fix this:",
