                                                                                                              "content": "Looking at the failing tests, I can see the issue. The tokenization is working correctly (preserving comments), but when we use `_py_ast_to_source` to reconstruct the AST, it's not preserving the tokens. The issue is that `_py_ast_to_source` generates fresh Python code from the AST, which doesn't include our tokens.\n\nLet me check how `_py_ast_to_source` is implemented:",
