                                                                                                                    "replies": [
                                                                                                                     {
                                                                                                                      "content": "You're absolutely right! Looking at the code, I can see that the token format was changed from using `;;;` delimiters to `__TOKEN__hexcontent__` format. Let me check where this happened:",
